  "texts": [
    "Recent activities are mainly focused on the definition of chill-down flow regimes and related heat transfer characteristics, to be able to correctly describe the phenomena and to develop adequate models for prediction.",
    "A large amount of work is done on ground, but chill-down in depots occurs in microgravity conditions.",
    "Some activities include test-bench and experiments to reproduce microgravity conditions 96, 100, 101.",
    "Chill-down process optimization is also a promising field of investigation, which aim at continuously improving the efficiency of cryogenic fluid applications.",
    "These two research activities are developed complementary with the common goal of reaching a comprehensive capability of chill-down management."
  ],
